longBusinessSummary: Enterprise Group, Inc. operates as an equipment rental and construction services company in Western Canada. The company primarily focuses on the specialty equipment rentals and service business. It rents trucks and heavy equipment, and flameless heating units, as well as offers oilfield infrastructure site services. It serves utility, energy, construction, and infrastructure industries. The company was formerly known as Enterprise Oilfield Group, Inc. and changed its name to Enterprise Group, Inc. in July 2012. Enterprise Group, Inc. was incorporated in 2004 and is headquartered in St. Albert, Canada.
